nodes.text: Corte Voss was a Twi'lek female smuggler who captained the light freighter Titan's Mercy and its crew of five, including the Jawa Kef. During the Imperial Period, Voss made a poor deal with the Gorensla, which lost her a large sum of money. She later attempted to cheat the Trandoshan arms dealer Thamoss on Nar Shaddaa.
